longBusinessSummary: Eastern Goldfields, Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in the acquisition, development, exploration, and mining of gold properties. Its mining operations are located primarily in the Barberton Greenstone Belt area of the Mpumalanga Province, South Africa. The company is based in San Diego, California.
